quran[75]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,Liswejesyani lina lya Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) Ŵapenani kusyene
  87,2,Aŵala ŵaŵagumbile (chilichose) ni kuchikolosya
  87,3,Soni Aŵala ŵaŵapimiile (chilichose mwachiichiŵeela) ni kuchijongolela (ku yaŵachipimileyo)
  87,4,Soni Aŵala ŵaakumesya mopo
  87,5,Ni kuwusyusya kuŵa wejumu ŵakupiililila
  87,6,Chitunsoomesye ni ngan'diŵalila
  87,7,"Ikaŵeje yasachile Allah, chisimu Jwalakwe jukumanyililaga yakuonechela ni yayikasasisika"
  87,8,Ni chitun'jepepachisye litala lyakwalukangana (lyakutendela yambone)
  87,9,Basi kumbusyani naga kumbusyako tikuŵe kwakamuchisya
  87,10,Talikumbusye mundu jwaakun'jogopa (Allah)
  87,11,Ni takuŵambale (mundu) jwakusakala nnope
  87,12,Ajula jwatakajinjile ku Moto Wekulungwa
  87,13,"Soni ngachija kumpata chiwa mwalakwemo, nambo soni ngaaja kuŵa ni umi (wambone)"
  87,14,Pamasile paapundile mundu jwaliswejesye (ntima wakwe)
  87,15,Ni akuŵa ali nkulikumbuchila Lina lya Ambujegwe (pakulikolanga) aku achiswaliji
  87,16,Nambo ŵanganyammwe nkulongosya umi wa duniya
  87,17,Kutendaga Akhera ni jambone nnope soni jandamo
  87,18,Chisimu yalakweyi yili mu ikalakala yandanda
  87,19,Ikalakala ya Ibrahima ni Musa
  88,1,"Ana jinyyiche abali ja chakuunichila (ŵandu ni yogoyo yakwe, jajili Kiyama)"
  88,2,Ngope sine lyele lisikulyo sichiŵa syakunyosyeka
  88,3,"Syasyapanganyisye masengo (gasambi ku duniya), syakupela (nikwaluka ku Akhera)"
  88,4,Sichijinjila ku Moto Wakupoteka nnope
  88,5,Sichimwesyedwa mu tutumule jwansemule kusyene
  88,6,Ngasakola ŵanganyao yakulya ikaŵeje miŵa janchongwe
  88,7,Jangajimbasya soni jangakamuchisya ku sala
  88,8,Ngope sine lyele lisikulyo sichiŵa m’chindimba
  88,9,Ligongo lya masengo gakwe (gambone) sichiŵa syakusengwa
  88,10,Ku Mbepo Japenani
  88,11,Ngasisija kupikana kwalakweko yangali mate
  88,12,Kweleko kwana tutumule jwakujilimaga
  88,13,Kweleko kwana itengu yauchimbichimbi yenyakulidwe
  88,14,Ni migawo jeŵichidwe (chilepe)
  88,15,Ni misago jejalidwe mu ntungo wambone
  88,16,Ni yakutandika yaofuofu yetandichidwe posepose
  88,17,Ana ngakujiona ngamiya yajatite kagumbidwe
  88,18,Ni liwunde yalyatite kanyakulidwe
  88,19,Ni matumbi yagatite kasimichidwe
  88,20,Ni litaka yalyatite katandichidwe
  88,21,"Basi kumbusyani, chisimu mmwejo ni nkukumbusya"
  88,22,Nganim'batu mmwe ŵakwakanganichisya ŵanganyao (chikulupi)
  88,23,Ikaŵeje jwatagalauche (kuleka masengo gambone) ni kufulu (kuleka Usilamu)
  88,24,Basi Allah tachinnagasya ni ilagasyo yekulungwa nnope
  88,25,Chisimu Kukwetu pe ni kwakuujila kwao
  88,26,Soni chisimu kuŵalanjidwa kwao kuli Nowe
  89,1,Ngukulumbila kumasikusiku
  89,2,Ni ilo likumi (yandanda yamwesi wa Mfungotatu)
  89,3,Ni (indu yayili) yiŵiliyiŵili kwisa soni (yayili) chimochimo
  89,4,Ni chilo ndema jachikuŵigula
  89,5,"Ana mu yalakweyi ngaŵa mwana kulumbila kwakwanila, kwa jwakwete lunda"
  89,6,Ana nganinyyiona yaŵatite Ambuje ŵenu kaape ipotesi ŵanya Adi
  89,7,Ŵa ku Irama; achalewulewu mpela misaati
  89,8,Ŵanganagumbidweje ŵane ŵanti chisawu ŵanganyao mu ilambo (ine)
  89,9,Ni ŵanya Asamuda ŵaŵaliji nkusokola maganga pachiŵata (chakuŵilanjikwa Wadi Qura kuŵa majumba gao)
  89,10,Kwisa soni Firiauna nsyene ichili (yakulimbanganyichisya uchimwene wakwe)
  89,11,Aŵala ŵana kusumbaga mpika mu ilambo (pakusakasya)
  89,12,Ni ŵatupiye mwalakwemo kuwatanganya
  89,13,Basi Ambuje ŵenu ŵapungulile ŵanganyao mitundu ja ilagasyo (yakupoteka nnope)
  89,14,"Chisimu Ambuje ŵenu aŵele Ŵang'unulila (masengo ga ŵandu, mwanti chachalipila mwaakupanganyichisya)"
  89,15,"Sano mundu ndema jaakun'dinga Ambujegwe pakunchimbichisya ni kumpa chindimba, basi akasatiji: “Ambuje ŵangu anjimbichisye (ligongo une nijwakuŵajilwa kupata yeleyi).”"
  89,16,"Nambo ndema jaakun'dinga pakunnandiyichisya lisiki lyakwe, akasatiji: “Ambuje ŵangu anjalwisye.”"
  89,17,Ngwamba! Nambo kuti ngankwatendelaga yaukoto ŵanache ŵawina
  89,18,Soni ngankuchisyanaga yaagaliisya masikini
  89,19,Ni nkulyaga chipanje chamalekwa kalye kakutunduka
  89,20,Ni nkuchinonyelaga soni chipanje kachinonyele kakupelenganya nnope
  89,21,Ngaŵa (mŵankutendelamo)! Ndema jalichisyajidwa litaka syajidwe-syajidwe
  89,22,"Ni kwika Ambuje ŵenu (Allah kukwiilanya magambo), Achimalaika ali ndandanda"
  89,23,"Ni kwikanajo lyele lisikulyo Jahannama! Lyele lisikulyo mundu tachikumbuchila (yaŵapanganyisye), nambo ana kuchinkamuchisya chichi kwele kumbuchilako"
  89,24,"Tachiti (pakuligamba): “Nkongwene! Bola ngalongosye (yambone yakungamuchisya) pa umi wangu (walelo uno).”"
  89,25,"Mwanti palyele lisikuli, pangali jwampaka apeleche ilagasyo mwatachipelechela (Allah)"
  89,26,Soni pangali jwampaka ataŵe mwatachitaŵila (Jwalakwe)
  89,27,E mmwe antima ŵakutulala
  89,28,Wujilani kwa Ambuje ŵenu n'di ŵakusengwa ni kunonyeledwa
  89,29,Jinjilani mwikuga lya achikapolo Ŵangu
  89,30,Soni jinjilani ku Mbepo Jangu